<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 Server Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 10rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #05a185;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .fun-message {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        a {
            color: #05a185;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 2px solid #05a185;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #05a185;
            color: white;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #05a185;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="error-code">:(</div>
    <div class="message">Server Error</div>
    <div class="fun-message">
        ¡Qué verguenza! Esto no debería estar pasando ...
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
